title: Invitation to Tecnotree’s Interim Report Q3/2015 presentation
text:
20 Oct, 2015 at 12.00 EEST 
Tecnotree will publish its Q3/2015 results on Thursday, 29 Oct 2015 at 8.30 am (EET). A press conference for analysts, investors and media will be held on Thursday, 29 Oct 2015 at 10.00 am in Hotel Scandic Simonkenttä, conference room Tapiola, 1 floor, address Simonkatu 9, Helsinki. The conference will be held in Finnish. The Q3/2015 interim report will be presented by Mr. Ilkka Raiskinen, CEO. The material will be available on the company website www.tecnotree.com after publication. Inform your participation latest by Tue 27 Oct 2015: investor.relations@tecnotree.com TECNOTREE CORPORATION
